content.text: Hi, I run a pet accessories brand in the UK. Looking to source custom dog harnesses - I found this on Alibaba as reference: https://www.alibaba.com/product/123456. Want 500 units with our logo. Can you help?

content.thinking: Pet dog harnesses, 500 units, custom logo, UK destination.

content.text:
Great to hear from you! Custom dog harnesses are a strong category — lots of factory options in China for that.

For 500 units with custom logo, you're looking at roughly *$3-7 per unit* depending on material (nylon webbing is cheapest, padded mesh mid-range, neoprene premium). Custom logo via heat transfer or woven label is standard at that quantity.

What material/style are you leaning toward — basic nylon, padded/breathable mesh, or something more premium?
